Measurement of τ polarization in W→τν decays with the ATLAS detector in pp collisions at \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
